      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAKOTA COURTNEY (5) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (17.51) at this track in a Grade 5 over 300m. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Makes plenty of appeal. BLUE MAJESTIC (1) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a second place finish (17.48) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. FUN EFFECTS (2) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (17.80) at this track behind Tralee Luna in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. The form out of her last race has been franked. Leading chance. BROOKLYN BANDIT (7) was out of placings last time (20.19) at Capalaba in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 8 lengths. Has already won out of this draw.",
